title: Hey waaaiiit a minute.
body:
https://am-a.akamaihd.net/image?f=https://news-a.akamaihd.net/public/images/articles/2018/october/821patchnotes/Janna_TFTR_Splash.jpg
Janna isn't not giving a fuck in this image, that's not allowed in non legendary skins.  Riot. What are you doing?

(To explain, Janna in all of her splash arts prior to this had a blank expression making it seem like she didn't give a fuck what was happening, her legendary Forecast was the sole exception until now.)
